en Problems – diachron, diskurshistorisch, kulturwissenschaftlich.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Jan 2023) 4aNarratologie. 4aNavigatio S. Brendani. 4aTractatus de Purgatorio S. Patricii. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Medieval.2bisacsh  aNavigatio S. Brendani.  aTractatus de Purgatorio S. Patricii.  anarratology.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2020 Part 1z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2020z9783110704532oZDB-23-DKU0 cEPUBz97831106810550 cprintz978311068013340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311068098040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110680980423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110680980/original  a978-3-11-069627-1  DG Plus DeG Package 2020 Part 1b2020  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2020  aZDB-23-DKUb2020